These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, videographer, freelancer
1. the videographer is on the far left##1
2. the paramedic is on the right of the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Job   | videographer | freelancer | paramedic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, chef, nurse
1. the nurse is on the far right##1
2. the architect is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Job   | architect | chef | nurse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, hiking, camping
1. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Hobby   | writing | hiking | camping |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-4::.
