2. the person drinking cola is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2      |   3   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | juice | cola |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, trike, taxi
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2  |  3   |
| Transport   | taxi | trike | subway |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, zombie, western
1. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | western | scientific | zombie |

